    <section>

        <h1 data-ref="media_support">
            Media Support<br><small><dfn>08099f0d-a38e-422a-8a0b-214d4808d7c8</dfn></small>
        </h1>

        <p>The attribute <var>08099f0d-a38e-422a-8a0b-214d4808d7c8</var> is an object or an array of objects that define what media properties supported by an application, such as screen sizes, resolution, aspect ratios and color.</p>

        <section>

            <h3>Example</h3>

            <pre class="prettyprint lang-json">{
  "min-width": "320px"
}</pre>

            <pre class="prettyprint lang-json">{
  "max-width": "800px",
  "max-width": "800px",
  "color": true
}</pre>

        </section>

        <h3>JSON Schema</h3>

        <pre data-attribute-schema="08099f0d-a38e-422a-8a0b-214d4808d7c8"></pre>

